headline: GTA Online
subtitle: On the Podium this Week: Armored Enus Paragon R
content:
Once you’re done sweating it out on the Music Locker’s dancefloor, head back aboveground to the lobby of the Diamond to give the Lucky Wheel a spin and walk away with GTA$, RP, clothing, mystery prizes and more.

This week’s top prize on the podium is an Armored Enus Paragon R wrapped in the Doing Busy Work livery – a presence that’s sure to intimidate anyone unfortunate enough to get stuck at the red light with you.
